实体音乐销量将出现 20 年来首次增长https://www.nme.com/news/music/physical-music-sales-set-for-first-increase-in-20-years-3775262?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=physical-music-sales-set- 20年来首次增长Laura MolloyMon, 15 Jul 2024 21:03:52 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3775262 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/A-customer-looks-through-a-rack-of-vinyl-records-at-the-HMV-store-on-Oxford-street-on-December-28-2023.-Credit_-Peter-Nicholls_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2023 年 12 月 28 日，一位顾客在牛津街的 HMV 商店里浏览黑胶唱片架。图片来源：Peter Nicholls/Getty Images" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/A-customer-looks-through-a-rack-of-vinyl-records-at-the-HMV-store-on-Oxford-street-on-December-28-2023.-Credit_-Peter-Nicholls_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/A-customer-looks-through-a-rack-of-vinyl-records-at-the-HMV-store-on-Oxford-street-on-December-28-2023.-Credit_-Peter-Nicholls_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/A-customer-looks-through-a-rack-of-vinyl-records-at-the-HMV-store-on-Oxford-street-on-December-28-2023.-Credit_-Peter-Nicholls_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/A-customer-looks-through-a-rack-of-vinyl-records-at-the-HMV-store-on-Oxford-street-on-December-28-2023.-Credit_-Peter-Nicholls_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/A-customer-looks-through-a-rack-of-vinyl-records-at-the-HMV-store-on-Oxford-street-on-December-28-2023.-Credit_-Peter-Nicholls_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/A-customer-looks-through-a-rack-of-vinyl-records-at-the-HMV-store-on-Oxford-street-on-December-28-2023.-Credit_-Peter-Nicholls_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>泰勒·斯威夫特、比莉·艾利什和《最后的晚宴》是实体销量最高的艺术家之一</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/physical-music-sales-set-for-first-increase-in-20-years-3775262">实体音乐销量将在 20 年来首次增长，</a>该消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/A-customer-looks-through-a-rack-of-vinyl-records-at-the-HMV-store-on-Oxford-street-on-December-28-2023.-Credit_-Peter-Nicholls_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2023 年 12 月 28 日，一位顾客在牛津街的 HMV 商店里浏览黑胶唱片架。图片来源：Peter Nicholls/Getty Images" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/A-customer-looks-through-a-rack-of-vinyl-records-at-the-HMV-store-on-Oxford-street-on-December-28-2023.-Credit_-Peter-Nicholls_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/A-customer-looks-through-a-rack-of-vinyl-records-at-the-HMV-store-on-Oxford-street-on-December-28-2023.-Credit_-Peter-Nicholls_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/A-customer-looks-through-a-rack-of-vinyl-records-at-the-HMV-store-on-Oxford-street-on-December-28-2023.-Credit_-Peter-Nicholls_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/A-customer-looks-through-a-rack-of-vinyl-records-at-the-HMV-store-on-Oxford-street-on-December-28-2023.-Credit_-Peter-Nicholls_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/A-customer-looks-through-a-rack-of-vinyl-records-at-the-HMV-store-on-Oxford-street-on-December-28-2023.-Credit_-Peter-Nicholls_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/A-customer-looks-through-a-rack-of-vinyl-records-at-the-HMV-store-on-Oxford-street-on-December-28-2023.-Credit_-Peter-Nicholls_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在多年被流媒体黯然失色之后，实体音乐的销量有望迎来二十年来的首次增长。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-and-record-store-day-see-highest-weekly-vinyl-sales-in-30-years-3752390">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 和 Record Store Day 创下 30 年来最高的每周黑胶唱片销量</a></strong></li></ul><p>人们对实体音乐收藏的兴趣重新燃起，达到了新的高度，<a href="https://www.officialcharts.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>官方排行榜公司</em></a>和<a href="https://www.bpi.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>BPI</em></a>报告称，2024 年前六个月实体专辑销量增长了 3.2%，售出 8,044,760 张。这标志着该行业自 2004 年开始转向数字音乐消费和流媒体以来首次出现增长。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift</a> ) 的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lyrics-tracklist-3619454">The Tortured Poets Department</a> 》是销量增长的最大贡献者，2024 年前 6 个月销量达 254,241 份。实体销量前 5 名的其他记录包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish</a> ) 的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/billie-eilish-hit-me-hard-and-soft-review-tracklist-lyrics-3756826">Hit Me</a> 》 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/billie-eilish-hit-me-hard-and-soft-review-tracklist-lyrics-3756826">《Hard and Soft</a> 》售出了 45,434 张， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party</a>的首张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-last-dinner-party-prelude-to-ecstasy-album-review-radar-3577784">Prelude To Ecstasy</a> 》（42,352 张）以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">Liam Gallagher</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-squire">John Squire</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/liam-gallagher-john-squire-tracklist-lyrics-3593699">同名专辑</a>（46,982 张）。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rod-stewart">罗德·斯图尔特 (Rod Stewart</a> ) 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jools-holland">朱尔斯·霍兰德 (Jools Holland)</a>的合作专辑“Swing Fever”销量达到 48,540 张，仅次于斯威夫特位居第二。</p><p>这一消息是在今年黑胶唱片销量呈上升趋势的基础上发布的。得益于唱片店日和同周发行的《The Tortured Poets Department》，四月份<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-and-record-store-day-see-highest-weekly-vinyl-sales-in-30-years-3752390">黑胶唱片销量创下三十年来最高的每周总销量</a>。<a href="https://www.officialcharts.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>官方排行榜公司</em></a>的数据显示，这两场活动共售出 269,134 张黑胶专辑和 37,656 张黑胶单曲，总计 306,791 份。</p><p>然而，随着许多艺术家现在发行实体专辑的新版本，更大的环境影响受到了质疑。今年早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-hits-out-at-artists-who-release-multiple-vinyl-formats-to-boost-album-sales-i-find-it-really-frustrating-3610898">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish) 批评了发行多种黑胶唱片格式以促进销量的艺术家</a>，称这种做法“浪费”。</p><p> “我们生活在这个时代，出于某种原因，对一些艺术家来说，制作各种不同的黑胶唱片和包装非常重要，”艾利什说，“这可以提高销量和数量，让他们赚更多的钱。”</p><p>她补充道：“它就在我们面前，人们却左右为难，”她补充道，“作为一个真正不遗余力追求可持续发展并尽我所能的人，我觉得这真的很令人沮丧。”可以并尝试让我团队中的每个人都参与可持续发展——然后世界上一些最伟大的艺术家制作了 40 种不同的乙烯基包装，这些包装具有不同的独特之处，只是为了让你继续购买更多。”</p><p>如今，这已成为行业内的普遍现象。斯威夫特的 2022 年 LP 《Midnights》 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-reveals-collectable-editions-of-midnights-on-cd-and-vinyl-3303014">以五种不同的版本出售</a>，最终成为自 20 世纪 80 年代以来首张黑胶唱片销量高于 CD 的专辑。</p><p>实体音乐日益流行的消息还传出， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/number-of-uk-independent-record-shops-hits-10-year-high-3597354">英国独立唱片店数量创10年来新高</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/uk-vinyl-sales-2023-reach-highest-level-since-1990-3563676">英国黑胶唱片销量创1990年以来最高水平</a>。</p><p>根据 BPI 的分析，“对黑胶唱片和其他物理格式音乐发行的需求不断增长”反映了“商业街音乐市场的蓬勃发展”。它还引用了独立唱片店的受欢迎程度以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hmvs-flagship-oxford-street-store-to-return-after-four-years-3436975">HMV 等商店的成功，该公司去年在伦敦牛津街重新开设了旗舰店</a>。在这场运动<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/our-price-share-more-details-of-their-plan-to-relaunch-iconic-music-store-3751981">中，英国标志性音乐商店 Our Price 在被迫关门 20 年后重新开业</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/physical-music-sales-set-for-first-increase-in-20-years-3775262">实体音乐销量将在 20 年来首次增长，</a>该消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
玛丽娜透露她正在制作第六张专辑https://www.nme.com/news/music/marina-reveals-she-is-working-on-her-sixth-album-3775252?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=marina-reveals-she-is-working-她的第六张专辑Anagricel DuranMon, 15 Jul 2024 20:33:14 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3775252 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Marina-Diamandis-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2024 年 7 月 13 日，玛丽娜·迪亚曼迪斯 (Marina Diamandis) 在英国伦敦海德公园举行的 BST 海德公园表演中为凯莉·米洛 (Kylie Minogue) 表演。 （乔·黑尔/雷德芬斯摄）" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Marina-Diamandis-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Marina-Diamandis-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Marina-Diamandis-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Marina-Diamandis-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Marina-Diamandis-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Marina-Diamandis-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我正在制作一张新唱片，我很喜欢它。它肯定会在明年发行”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marina-reveals-she-is-working-on-her-sixth-album-3775252">玛丽娜透露她正在制作第六张专辑的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Marina-Diamandis-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2024 年 7 月 13 日，玛丽娜·迪亚曼迪斯 (Marina Diamandis) 在英国伦敦海德公园举行的 BST 海德公园表演中为凯莉·米洛 (Kylie Minogue) 表演。 （乔·黑尔/雷德芬斯摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Marina-Diamandis-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Marina-Diamandis-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Marina-Diamandis-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, http